name: Thanksgiving Any Day Rollups
author: Mary Sherwood Dreibelbis
summary: With delicious holiday ingredients, you can have an easy, healthy, and portable taste of Thanksgiving any day! Sliced, cooked turkey can be substituted for the Tofurky® if desired.
ingredients: ½ (8 ounce) package shredded Cheddar cheese
12  meatless turkey-flavored deli slices (such as Tofurky®), chopped
salt and ground black pepper to taste
directions: Combine cream cheese and Cheddar cheese in a food processor; process until blended
Add meatless turkey slices, cranberries, pecans, celery, green onions, chives, salt, and black pepper
Spread cream cheese mixture onto each tortilla and roll up
Serve immediately or refrigerate until serving time
